{"type":null,"faqId":45102,"title":"如何使用B2进行智能解锁？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.27708334in;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.06875in;}\n.s3{color:black;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.29166666in;margin-left:1.0006944in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.29166666in;margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{text-indent:0.21875in;margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p6{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>进入设置—锁屏和密码。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=164053\" style=\"width:1.3243055in;height:2.3611112in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">2.  </span><span>进入智能解锁。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=164054\" style=\"width:1.3270833in;height:2.3611112in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">3.  </span><span>点击设置锁屏密码，按照提示设置任意一种锁屏密码（如果之前已经设置过锁屏密码，可忽略此步骤）。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=164055\" style=\"width:1.3277777in;height:2.3611112in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">4.  </span><span>密码设置成功后，点解添加用于解锁的设备。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=164056\" style=\"width:1.3277777in;height:2.3611112in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">5.  </span><span>点击设备配对，将B2手环与手机配对，前提B2处于配对模式（如何进入配对模式参考FAQ1，如果之前B2已经与手机建立连接可忽略此步骤）。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=164057\" style=\"width:1.3277777in;height:2.3611112in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">6.  </span><span>点击已连接的设备，将其设置为解锁设备，图6、图7。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=164058\" style=\"width:1.3277777in;height:2.3611112in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=164059\" style=\"width:1.3277777in;height:2.3611112in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s3\">至此，灭屏亮屏后，滑动解锁无需输入之前设置的锁屏密码，直接进入主界面。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\"></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"603","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442409588000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":14,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"B,智能解锁","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}